      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all restoration fans and DIY experts! This vehicle is the perfect project for anyone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to its prime. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic and affordable foundation for a dedicated owner to make it their own!",
