    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like a total dream. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale, so I've priced it to move! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
