    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom-ready condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple without any creasing or bolster wear, and the factory 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every electronic component, from the responsive infotainment system to the multi-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder of exhaustive service records, documenting every oil change and inspection performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. Recently fitted with a fresh set of premium tires and having undergone a complete preventive fluid service, it needs absolutely nothing but a new home. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
